### Admin Login
POST http://localhost:4000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email":"admin@gmail.com",
    "password":"admin"
}


### Admin Logout
GET http://localhost:4000/auth/logout


### Read all articles written by authors
GET http://localhost:4000/admin-api/articles


### Modify user status (enable / disable)
PUT http://localhost:4000/admin-api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "userId":"69b4df2cfcdf7a0bccfc9076",
    "isUserActive": false
}
